{\b0 \cf21 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf21 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Florida state courts had jurisdiction to hear real estate company\rquote s action for writ of mandamus and declaratory relief to force county property appraiser to issue public records without licensing agreement, even though county appraiser\rquote s defense was based on federal copyright law; case arose under Florida\rquote s public records law, and copyright was not an essential matter of the claim. 
}
