Op. Att\rquote y Gen. Fla. 03\u8211\'3f42 (2003)
}
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&pubNum=0003636&cite=FLAOPATTYGEN03&originatingDoc=I27afd7e743d911d98915dbcd77ee80bc&refType=DE&fi=co_pp_sp_3636_42&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.CustomDigest)#co_pp_sp_3636_42" }{\fldrslt 
{\b0 \cf23 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Op. Att\rquote y Gen. Fla. 03\u8211\'3f42 (2003)
}}}
{\b0 \cf21 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 (stating that in the absence of statutory authorization and \u8220\'3fin light of Florida\rquote s Public Records Law, Palm Beach County is not authorized to obtain copyright protection and require license agreements for its Geographic Information Systems (GIS) and related data in order to regulate and authorize redistribution of these materials for commercial use\u8221\'3f); 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=0103094737&pubNum=0004253&originatingDoc=I27afd7e743d911d98915dbcd77ee80bc&refType=DE&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.CustomDigest)" }{\fldrslt 
{\b0 \cf23 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Op. Att\rquote y Gen. Fla. 88\u8211\'3f23 (1988)
}}}
{\b0 \cf21 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 (reciting that State Attorneys may not, without statutory authority, assert copyright in training films they produced); 
}
{\b0 \cf21 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf21 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
accord
}
}
{\b0 \cf21 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 
}
